channel.title: Anyone have this type of Delete Void?
channel.description: What type of void I'm talking about if when you click on an object or something it deletes a certain object, IE if you clicked on a door it would delete it. Everytime I try what I made I d/c.. And no, it's not Fedexer's delete object's release you have to specify the coords with that. With mine you are spawning the object with an item and you can delete your object.
